title: James Harden, Tom Brady, Bill Belichick, and Jared Goff
itunes:title: James Harden, Tom Brady, Bill Belichick, and Jared Goff
description:
Colin explains why he's not impressed with the current play of Houston Rockets G James Harden, why New England Patriots QB Tom Brady is an icon among icons, why all the credit shouldn't be given to Patriots HC Bill Belichick, and why he is impressed with Los Angeles Rams QB Jared Goff. Guests include Eddie House, Greg Cosell, Rob Parker, Greg Jennings, & Jason McIntyre.
